Subclasses of SummaryTableModel in edu.umaryland.igs.idea
 class PairwiseSummaryTableModel
          PairwiseSummaryTableModel is the subclass of SummaryTableModel used for tables derived from pairwise IDEA analyses (those for which all datasets have exactly two sequences).
 class StandardSummaryTableModel
          StandardSummaryTableModel is the subclass of SummaryTableModel used for tables derived from non-pairwise IDEA analyses (those with at least one dataset having three or more sequences).
